title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 13 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 13 2022
description:
Democrats begin to put pressure on Fetterman from hiding from Oz in Pennsylvania. Kari Lake's opponent in Arizona says she won't debate, Lake eviscerates her. Buck sees a Trump-Biden rematch in 2024. Jill Biden says she hasn't spoken to Joe, but he should keep going. Julie Kelly joins Clay and Buck with her take on the Mar-a-Lago investigation. She predicts the Biden DOJ will indict Trump before the election and seek jail time. Howard Stern thinks Trump sold nuclear secrets to the Russians.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
